Why did you choose an apartment in a new building?
We were looking for a carefree apartment, where most of the care of the property is provided by the administrator.
The condition was sufficient parking spaces and an elevator in the house, which basically disqualified the older buildings.
Not to mention problematic acoustics in old houses, problems with swinging the floor, high energy intensity and the like.
