Changes are not planned, most of the modifications after the move-in took place in the level of the shading and accommodation of the terraces.
Perhaps the only complaint is to the floor, when the walnut wood turns out to be too delicate for the household with the dog.
The word of architects, Ing. arch. Lenka Langerov<0xC3><0xA1> and MgA. Kamila Hornychov<0xC3><0xA1>, author of the realization.
