How much money will the courier receive after the shipment has been successfully delivered to the hand?
The courier determines the price and gets the full amount he asks for.
The sender is charged a few percent extra for mediating the contact.
This money is our profit, but it is only a few percent, because we want to push on the volume.
The courier can also not accuse that he did not deliver the shipment when he actually delivered it, the receipt and delivery is verified using QR codes.
