Whether in relation to the size or content of the package?
You can transport anything.
We have three sizes, small as a butter cube, medium as a plateau of eggs, and large as a bass beer.
After that, there is no more restriction and if someone has a place in the car, they can take the refrigerator.
Plus, the sender has the option to take a picture of the package in the app, so that the courier can see what he wants.
